[normal] to ensure capacity development for effective inclusion
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]8.5
[normal] 
[normal]C
[normal]ommit to 
[normal]ensuring 
[normal]accountability by requiring 
[normal]that 
[normal]disability disaggregated data is collected for all programmes, including those funded [bold]through[bold] Bilateral and Multilateral Aid.[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]8.6
[normal] 
[normal]E[bold]nsure [bold]the[bold] 
[normal]social[bold] and psychosocial[bold] impacts of disability such as stigma and discriminatory behaviour are appropriately addressed[bold] within an equity and inclusion strategy[bold].
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]8.7
[normal] 
[normal]Include[bold] ‘prevention of disability’ [bold]as an important 
[normal]approach 
[normal]within its disability policy, 
